  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Recruitment Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Why Join MCI?</strong></p><p>At MCI Career Services, we don’t just sell a service — we connect talents with opportunities and help clients build strong teams. If you love meeting people, enjoy closing deals, and want a career with uncapped earning potential, this role is for you.</p><p><strong>Summary</strong></p><ul><li><p>Basic Salary Range: $2500 - $3500</p></li><li><p>Working Hours: Mon - Fri (8.30am - 6pm)</p></li><li><p>Location: Jurong East (Near MRT!)</p></li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Get (Benefits)</strong></p><ul><li><p>Monthly Sales Commission</p></li><li><p>Bi-yearly Increment Opportunity</p></li><li><p>Incentive Trip</p></li><li><p>Continuous learning, coaching & career development</p></li><li><p>Strong internal support from BD + TA team</p></li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li><p>Screen and shortlist candidates according to hiring requirements</p></li><li><p>Coordinate interviews and manage end-to-end candidate communications</p></li><li><p>Provide timely updates and ensure a positive candidate experience</p></li><li><p>Partner with stakeholders to support recruitment and workforce needs</p></li><li><p>Advise on selection best practices and hiring processes</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with TAFEP guidelines and maintain accurate recruitment records</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum Diploma qualification, preferably in Human Resources, Business, or related fields</p></li><li><p>Strong organisational skills with good attention to detail</p></li><li><p>Eagerness to learn and develop within the recruitment and talent acquisition field</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated and goal-oriented, with the ability to work in a fast-paced environment</p></li></ul><p>Applicants who possess relevant experience for the above responsibilities are most welcome to apply. If you do not possess the above experience, your application will still be considered on individual merits and you may be contacted for other opportunities.</p><p>Please submit your updated resume in MS Words format by using the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by the company relating to this job application.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf</a></p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p><strong>Jong Si Xiang</strong><br /><strong>Registration Number: R25157567</strong><br /><strong>EA Licence No: 06C2859 (MCI Career Services Pte Ltd)</strong></p>",
